'''Dirk de Villiers''' (26 Nyakanga 1924 - 28 Ukuboza 2009), yari umukinnyi wa filime wo [[Afurika y’Epfo|muri Afurika y'Epfo]] <ref>https://www.imdb.com/name/nm0222562/bio</ref>.  Ufatwa nk'umukinnyi wa filime wamamaye cyane na 'Godfather' mu nganda za firime zo muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'Epfo, de Villiers yakoze filime nyinshi zishimwa cyane mu mwuga umaze imyaka irenga mirongo itandatu<ref>https://artsandculture.google.com/entity/dirk-devilliers/m0cj10sd?hl=en</ref>.  

== Ubuzima bwite ==
Yavutse ku ya 26 Nyakanga 1924 mu isambu ya Villieria i Douglas, mu majyaruguru ya Cape, [[Afurika y’Epfo|muri Afurika y'Epfo]] mu muryango ufite barumuna be batanu<ref>https://mubi.com/cast/dirk-de-villiers</ref>. Nyina yapfuye afite imyaka ine naho se ni umuhinzi wakomeje guhinga yarazwe na Cornelius Valkenburg de Villiers. Nyina amaze gupfa, Dirk na murumuna we Niel boherejwe kwa nyirasenge <ref>https://www.amazon.com/PW-Afrikaans-Dirk-Villiers/dp/062402069X</ref>. Nyuma yaje gukurira ku nkombe z'umugezi wa Vaal aho yagiye mu mashuri menshi yo muri Jagersfontein, Marquard na Betelehemu<ref>https://www.tvguide.com/celebrities/dirk-de-villiers/credits/3030388066/</ref> . 

Yashakanye n'umukinnyi wa filime Addy kuva 1950 kugeza yahukanye mu 1973. Abashakanye babyaranye abana batanu barimo Gys de Villiers . Gys kandi ni umukinnyi w'icyamamare akaba n'umwanditsi w'amakinamico muri sinema no muri [[Afurika y’Epfo|Afurika]] y'Epfo. Yagiranye umubano na Miems Swanepoel imyaka mike kuva 1992.<ref>https://www.thetvdb.com/people/7895508</ref> 

Ku ya 24 Ukuboza 2009, yahuye n'indwara y'umutima maze yihutira kujya mu bitaro by'Urwibutso rwa Chris Barnard i Cape Town. Icyakora, yapfuye ku ya 28 Ukuboza 2009 afite imyaka 89, azize indwara y'ibihaha no kunanirwa k'umutima.<ref>https://artsandculture.google.com/entity/dirk-devilliers/m0cj10sd?hl=en</ref>  

== Umwuga ==
Mu 1942, de Villiers yatangiye gukina amakinamico menshi ya Johannesburg [[Ikinyafurikansi|Afrikaans]] Amateur Abakinnyi (JAATS). Hanyuma yashinze ishyirahamwe ryamakinamico hamwe na Schalk Theron. Hamwe n'ikinamico, yize ibijyanye n'ubukanishi, aho yaje gukorera ku cyambu cya Cape Town. Hanyuma yagiye i Londres mu masomo y’ubuhanga bwo mu nyanja. Amaze kugaruka, yabaye injeniyeri w'ubwato<ref>https://www.afrikanergeskiedenis.co.za/dirk-de-villiers-1924-2009/</ref>.

Yatangiye umwuga wa film nkumukinnyi wa film ''Kruger Millions'' iyobowe na Ivan Hall. Muri filime, yakinnye nk'umuhemu wo mu mutwe wa Cavalier wiyahuye. Yakinnye kandi muri firime ,,, Kniediep, Kruger miljoene en Stadig oor die klippe. ''Tunga niggie yanjye'', ''Kavaliers'' . Yayoboye filime ye yambere ''yumukobwa Jy Is My Liefling'' . Iyi filime yakinnye na Franz Marx mu nshingano ze za mbere na Min Shaw. Nyuma yo gutsinda mubucuruzi muri firime, yakoze firime ''zamamaye, Die Geheim Van Nantes'' . Filime yahinduwe na serivise izwi cyane ya Springbok Radio, ikinwamo amajwi yose. Mu 1968 yakoze firime ye yambere yuzuye, ''You Are My Darling'' kandi ashingwa nkumukinnyi wa firime wabigize umwuga<ref>https://www.afrikanergeskiedenis.co.za/dirk-de-villiers-1924-2009/</ref>.<ref>https://www.researchgate.net/publication/307845922_Public_Theology_in_pluralistic_societies_Lessons_from_the_theology_of_Etienne_de_Villiers</ref>  

Mu 1972, de Villiers yakoze firime ishimishije ''My Broer Se Bril'' . Hanyuma mu 1974, yayoboye filime ebyiri ''Met Liefde Van Adele'' na ''Nyiricyubahiro'' . Hagati aho, mu 1976, yakoze filime ye ya mbere ''yamamaye ku'' ''rwego mpuzamahanga Glenda'' na Die diamantjagters. Mu 1978, yakoze ikinamico ''yerekanwe na euthanasiya yitwa Besluit om te sterf'' . Hagati aho, de Villiers yashinze Roodepoort Amateur Theatre Organisation (RATO). Zimwe muri firime yakunzwe cyane zirimo: ''Geheim van Nantes'', ''Kalahari Harry'', ''Die Spaanse Vlieg'', ''Daan en Doors op die dieggins'', ''Broer se bril'', ''Tant Ralie se losieshuis'', ''Die lewe sonder jou'', ''Die drie Van der Merwes'', ''Met liefde van Adéle'', ''My naam ni Dingetjie'', ''Witblits en Peach Brandy'', ''Dingetjie en Idi'', ''Die wit sluier en Kaalgat tussen bapfa daisies'' .<ref>https://www.imdb.com/title/tt2032540/characters/nm0222562</ref><ref>https://www.scriling.com/smdb/people/983703/dirk-de-villiers</ref><ref>https://www.radiotimes.com/movie-guide/b-8pa2lq/witblits-peach-brandy/</ref>  

